snippet.title: Goeland early gameplay peek
snippet.description:
I'm thrilled to unveil "Goeland" - my brand new game now available for wishlisting on Steam!
Be a part of the journey by adding Goeland to your wishlist today!
Let's soar together! 🐦

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2531840/Goeland?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=reveal8mar&utm_medium=social&utm_content=video
